# VMX Controller Protocol

Each command must end with a newline.

## Base commands

    GET_PROTOCOL
    PING
    GET_INFO
    READ_ADC_SCALE
    POWER_VOLTAGE
    STATUS
    CHANNEL_INFO <channel>
    CHANNEL_STATE <channel>
    CHANNEL_RELEASE <channel>
    RELEASE_ALL
    SAFE_STOP
    SERVER_STOP
    QUIT

## DIO

    DIO_OPEN_OUT <channel>
    DIO_OPEN_IN <channel>
    DIO_WRITE <channel> <0|1>
    DIO_READ <channel>

## PWM

    PWM_OPEN <channel> <frequency_hz>
    PWM_WRITE <channel> <0-255>
    PWM_READ <channel>

## Encoder

    ENCODER_OPEN <channel_a> <channel_b>
    ENCODER_READ <channel>
    ENCODER_DIRECTION <channel>
    ENCODER_PERIOD <channel>
    ENCODER_RESET <channel>

## Input capture

    INPUT_CAPTURE_OPEN <channel_a> <channel_b>
    INPUT_CAPTURE_READ <channel>
    INPUT_CAPTURE_STATUS <channel>
    INPUT_CAPTURE_RESET <channel>

    PWM_CAPTURE_OPEN <channel>
    PWM_CAPTURE_READ <channel>
    PWM_CAPTURE_RESET <channel>

## Analog

    ANALOG_OPEN <channel>
    ANALOG_READ <channel>

    ACCUMULATOR_OPEN <channel>
    ACCUMULATOR_READ <channel>
    ACCUMULATOR_COUNTER_READ <channel>
    ACCUMULATOR_COUNTER_RESET <channel>

    ANALOG_TRIGGER_OPEN <channel> <high> <low> <STATE|RISING|FALLING>
    ANALOG_TRIGGER_READ <channel>

## UART

    UART_OPEN <tx_channel> <rx_channel> <baudrate>
    UART_AVAILABLE <channel>
    UART_WRITE_HEX <channel> <hex_data>
    UART_READ_HEX <channel> <max_bytes>
    UART_RELEASE <channel>

## SPI

    SPI_OPEN <clk> <miso> <mosi> <cs> <bitrate> <mode>
    SPI_WRITE_HEX <channel> <hex_data>
    SPI_READ_HEX <channel> <byte_count>
    SPI_TRANSACTION_HEX <channel> <hex_data>
    SPI_RELEASE <channel>

## I2C

    I2C_OPEN <sda_channel> <scl_channel>
    I2C_WRITE_HEX <channel> <device_address> <register_address> <hex_data>
    I2C_READ_HEX <channel> <device_address> <register_address> <byte_count>
    I2C_TRANSACTION_HEX <channel> <device_address> <tx_hex> <rx_count>
    I2C_RELEASE <channel>

## One-Wire LED array

    LED_ARRAY_OPEN <channel> <pixels> <RGB|RBG|GRB|GBR|BRG|BGR>
    LED_ARRAY_SET_PIXEL <channel> <index> <r> <g> <b>
    LED_ARRAY_GET_PIXEL <channel> <index>
    LED_ARRAY_FILL <channel> <r> <g> <b>
    LED_ARRAY_SHOW <channel>
    LED_ARRAY_CLEAR <channel>
    LED_ARRAY_RELEASE <channel>

## navX / IMU

    IMU_STATUS
    IMU_ORIENTATION
    IMU_QUATERNION
    IMU_LINEAR_ACCEL
    IMU_RAW
    IMU_VELOCITY
    IMU_DISPLACEMENT
    IMU_ENVIRONMENT
    IMU_ZERO_YAW
    IMU_RESET_DISPLACEMENT

## Watchdog

    WATCHDOG_STATUS
    WATCHDOG_CONFIG <timeout_ms> <0|1>
    WATCHDOG_FEED
    WATCHDOG_EXPIRE
